{"ja451:0.1":"Jataka ","ja451:0.2":"Dasakanipata ","ja451:0.3":"Catudvaravagga ","ja451:0.4":"13. Cakkavakajataka ","ja451:1.1":"“Vannava abhiruposi, ","ja451:1.2":"ghano sanjatarohito; ","ja451:1.3":"Cakkavaka suruposi, ","ja451:1.4":"vippasannamukhindriyo. ","ja451:2.1":"Pathinam pavusam maccham, ","ja451:2.2":"balajam munjarohitam; ","ja451:2.3":"Gangaya tire nisinno, ","ja451:2.4":"evam bhunjasi bhojanam”. ","ja451:3.1":"“Na vahametam bhunjami, ","ja451:3.2":"Jangalanodakani va; ","ja451:3.3":"Annatra sevalapanaka, ","ja451:3.4":"Etam me samma bhojanam”. ","ja451:4.1":"“Na vahametam saddahami, ","ja451:4.2":"cakkavakassa bhojanam; ","ja451:4.3":"Ahampi samma bhunjami, ","ja451:4.4":"game loniyateliyam. ","ja451:5.1":"Manussesu katam bhattam, ","ja451:5.2":"sucim mamsupasecanam; ","ja451:5.3":"Na ca me tadiso vanno, ","ja451:5.4":"cakkavaka yatha tuvam”. ","ja451:6.1":"“Sampassam attani veram, ","ja451:6.2":"himsayam manusim pajam; ","ja451:6.3":"Utrasto ghasasi bhito, ","ja451:6.4":"tena vanno tavediso. ","ja451:7.1":"Sabbalokaviruddhosi, ","ja451:7.2":"dhanka papena kammuna; ","ja451:7.3":"Laddho pindo na pineti, ","ja451:7.4":"tena vanno tavediso. ","ja451:8.1":"Ahampi samma bhunjami, ","ja451:8.2":"ahimsam sabbapaninam; ","ja451:8.3":"Appossukko nirasanki, ","ja451:8.4":"asoko akutobhayo. ","ja451:9.1":"So karassu anubhavam, ","ja451:9.2":"vitivattassu siliyam; ","ja451:9.3":"Ahimsaya cara loke, ","ja451:9.4":"piyo hohisi mammiva. ","ja451:10.1":"Yo na hanti na ghateti, ","ja451:10.2":"na jinati na japaye; ","ja451:10.3":"Mettamso sabbabhutesu, ","ja451:10.4":"veram tassa na kenaci”ti. ","ja451:11.1":"Cakkavakajatakam terasamam. "}